{
  "texts": [
    "The WikiGold dataset [36] and the WiNER dataset [37] for training models to identify named entities in Wikipedia.",
    "NCBI-Disease dataset for identifying disease mentions in the biomedical domain [38].",
    "N 3 is a corpus for named entity recognition and disambiguation [39].",
    "SCI-ERC dataset for scientific information extraction [40].",
    "And NNE, a fine-grained nested named entity recognition dataset based on the BBN dataset [41]."
  ]
}